{"tid":1695341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"良心警/黃警同埋佢地身邊既人處境非常危險","createTime":"2019-11-05T14:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T15:13:44.000Z","uid":65378,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3e74f2886be014f2698282e2b5cbb70195b625b8","tid":1695341,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:45:30.000Z","msg":"借朋友acct出post <br />\n我身邊有位做前線警員既朋友，平時會通風報信d狗既行縱、俾料老豆搵仔。<br />\n<br />\n最近佢呀妹俾狗上門搭左，準備提堂告暴動、傷人等等既罪名。而佢呀妹的確係有去發夢，但唔係企得好前果d，亦冇玩過神獸魔法等等，唔會大機會因為係現場而被人Target。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講係狗隊內部係到掃鬼，然後再跟蹤佢身邊既人，搜證拉人。所以上門拉人果下已經有哂證據，過兩日已經可以提堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽到真係覺得好心酸，可能連登唔會覺得仲有良心警既存在，亦都fc唔到，但我都想係到提提佢地/佢地身邊既人真係要好好保護自己，出去發夢唔好留有任何俾人認到既特徵、覺得俾人跟蹤就要停止發夢一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b6c658365b76e3886c05f2d1a0b07922c74b50","tid":1695341,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"292ec68de6681eea20f62aeb7ccbf582c869a4cf","tid":1695341,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0260e3033946c0d04d20e9caca53030a6cf646ea","tid":1695341,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:46:07.00